name: hollybathing
description:
His name is wexi, He is relaxing and bathing and playing his violin, accompanied by some drink and a cat.

This is like a person who is in the bathroom enjoying his time to pamper himself, such as singing and whatever it is like there are no walls or obstacles around him and enjoying his day when he is in the bathroom.

I hope wexi will still feel comfortable and happy even though he is out of his bathing place.
